{"tid":2515373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"業績達標 Elon Musk將可再獲價值324億美元股票期權獎勵","createTime":"2021-05-04T02:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:49:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"772cc5761273f2ae4ca4ed3e61aa4be3b13398f1","tid":2515373,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"本就在全球巨富之列的馬斯克(Elon Musk)可能憑藉特斯拉(Tesla Inc., TSLA)股票期權再入袋324億美元。<br />\n<br />\n2018年獲批的馬斯克的薪酬方案包含一系列裡程碑要求，據上周五晚間提交的證券披露資訊，在這家電動汽車製造商實現了該方案中董事會所設相關目標的大約一半之後，馬斯克拿到手的股票期權收益價值324億美元。特斯拉在上周的另一份證券公告中表示，該公司很快就會達到其他一些目標，屆時馬斯克將被授予另外大約108億美元期權。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉三年前為馬斯克制定的股票期權發放獎勵計劃共涉及1.013億股股票，經拆股因素調整後，當時特斯拉的股價約為70美元。因此，馬斯克現已獲得的總共5,066萬股特斯拉股票期權的行權價為70.01美元。特斯拉股價上周五收盤報709.44美元。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/cn.wsj.com/amp/articles/%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC324%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%258D%258E%25E5%258B%25B5-11620013814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2F%2525E9%2525A6%2525AC%2525E6%252596%2525AF%2525E5%252585%25258B%2525E5%25258F%2525AF%2525E5%252586%25258D%2525E7%25258D%2525B2%2525E5%252583%2525B9%2525E5%252580%2525BC324%2525E5%252584%252584%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%252585%252583%2525E7%25259A%252584%2525E8%252582%2525A1%2525E7%2525A5%2525A8%2525E6%25259C%25259F%2525E6%2525AC%25258A%2525E7%25258D%25258E%2525E5%25258B%2525B5-11620013814&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=3c9ef8a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/cn.wsj.com/amp/articles/%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC324%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%258D%258E%25E5%258B%25B5-11620013814</a>"},{"pid":"28d7d7d11850bff233132b4882e95078310647f4","tid":2515373,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"自己送比自己"},{"pid":"3b5bc35184e9bdf1ab6b70baef231a1681984979","tid":2515373,"uid":101485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28d7d7d11850bff233132b4882e95078310647f4","tid":2515373,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"自己送比自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"自己封利是比自己 多謝阿爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}